		{
			"id":"8e7e150c5e1d23f5",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"用言：形容词，形容动词，动词，助动词，小句子",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":70,
			"y":-469,
			"width":460,
			"height":60,
			"color":"2"
		},
		{
			"id":"c6cbdc3e603ddf0e",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"连体形（な），终止形（だ）只有形容动词不同。两种词都没有命令形。",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-560,
			"y":1660,
			"width":260,
			"height":100
		},
		{
			"id":"f8fc0c6520fabfce",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"未然形特别少见",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-560,
			"y":1420,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{"id":"1c2fdf0ac323ebf4","type":"file","file":"日语学习/语法系统梳理/附件/{EED3D5C1-4001-47D9-8497-F487BF865EBB}.png","x":-882,"y":873,"width":265,"height":607},
		{
			"id":"ace7f4287393f3ac",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"连体修饰，连用修饰",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":1640,
			"y":-800,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{"id":"0366bb737407ca15","type":"file","file":"日语学习/语法系统梳理/附件/{136B9598-6B31-4CAB-8190-65A9EB44DAD7}.png","x":1980,"y":-893,"width":400,"height":247},
		{
			"id":"0e55e8b3be6d07fb",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"で只能表达中顿，に是作为副词修饰用言",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-540,
			"y":1060,
			"width":260,
			"height":60,
			"color":"2"
		},
		{"id":"e42220179bfa3c95","type":"file","file":"日语学习/语法系统梳理/附件/{BE07DBE4-664F-4C18-AB58-936122FC4CB9}.png","x":1980,"y":-560,"width":285,"height":400},
		{
			"id":"32733e30cff40635",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"副词可以直接修饰用言",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":2380,
			"y":-460,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"1a9bf6e56097d8ea",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"注意形容动词用と修饰的特殊情况",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":2380,
			"y":-360,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"e7f361042d742d56",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"名词+格助词 也可以当做连用词",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":2380,
			"y":-240,
			"width":320,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"09f4e718244ed39c",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"样态 传闻 推定 比拟",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-5040,
			"y":-2080,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"ccbdb8a1c6163ea0",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"看起来，听说，推定，比拟",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-4700,
			"y":-2080,
			"width":290,
			"height":60
		},
		{"id":"308d5fc74115a644","type":"file","file":"日语学习/语法系统梳理/附件/{3EE3C33D-B695-43D1-9DBC-D00421576403}.png","x":-4340,"y":-2120,"width":382,"height":418},
		{
			"id":"b1c03406cb3db0ea",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"で只作为终止，に作为副词",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":2380,
			"y":-560,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{"id":"e8c6bec257a5f12a","type":"file","file":"日语学习/语法系统梳理/附件/{11935EC8-FCE5-4F6E-A06D-FDAEE777A199}.png","x":-4340,"y":-1680,"width":382,"height":400},
		{
			"id":"19fcb23cb3e042ad",
